cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new classification model based on information theoretic concepts, specifically Renyi's entropy and Cauchy-Schwarz Divergence. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
